<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HTML Basic Tags - Complete Demo</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>HTML Basic Tags - Complete Example</h1>
    
    <h2>1. Headings</h2>
    <h1>Heading 1</h1>
    <h2>Heading 2</h2>
    <h3>Heading 3</h3>
    <h4>Heading 4</h4>
    <h5>Heading 5</h5>
    <h6>Heading 6</h6>

    <h2>2. Paragraph & Text Formatting</h2>
    <p>Ye ek normal paragraph hai.</p>
    <p><strong>Bold text</strong> aur <em>Italic text</em></p>
    <p><u>Underline</u> aur <del>Deleted text</del></p>
    <p><small>Small text</small> aur <mark>Highlighted text</mark></p>
    <p>Superscript: X<sup>2</sup> | Subscript: H<sub>2</sub>O</p>

    <h2>3. Lists</h2>
    <h3>Ordered List (Numbered)</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>Pehla item</li>
        <li>Dusra item</li>
        <li>Teesra item</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Unordered List (Bullets)</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Chai</li>
        <li>Samose</li>
        <li>Pakode</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Links & Images</h2>
    <a href="https://github.com/shivampatel0011" target="_blank">Mera GitHub Profile</a><br><br>
    
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x200" alt="Placeholder Image" width="400">

    <h2>5. Table</h2>
    <table border="1">
        <tr>
            <th>Name</th>
            <th>Branch</th>
            <th>Year</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Shivam Lodhi</td>
            <td>Computer Science</td>
            <td>Final Year</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>6. Forms</h2>
    <form>
        <label for="name">Naam:</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Apna naam likho"><br><br>
        
        <label for="email">Email:</label>
        <input type="email" id="email"><br><br>
        
        <label>Gender:</label>
        <input type="radio" name="gender"> Male
        <input type="radio" name="gender"> Female<br><br>
        
        <label>Hobbies:</label><br>
        <input type="checkbox"> Coding
        <input type="checkbox"> Farming
        <input type="checkbox"> Trading<br><br>
        
        <button type="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>

    <h2>7. Other Important Tags</h2>
    <blockquote>Ye ek quote hai - Hard work beats talent.</blockquote>
    
    <pre>
    Yeh pre tag hai
    Isme formatting preserve hoti hai
    </pre>

    <code>console.log("Hello World");</code>

    <hr>
    <p>Ye horizontal line hai (hr tag)</p>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Shivam Lodhi - HTML Learning</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
